edu.cmu.tetrad.data

Class VerticalIntDataBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.tetrad.data.VerticalIntDataBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataBox, TetradSerializable, Serializable

    public class VerticalIntDataBox
extends Object
implements DataBox
    Stores a 2D array of int data. Note that the missing value marker for this box is -99.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
